    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the overview. i guess i'm just wondering why certain people think it should be in the school at all instead of just at home. it feels like some people act like the school *has* to do this for it to be \"right,\" while others think it's actually harmful. do you think the school is just following a standard educational necessity, or is there more to it?",
